OL,7,FWATCH: Wartime hero who saved
OL,8,FCardiff's City Hall from burning down
OL,9,Fmore than 80 years ago is honoured on
OL,10,Fhis birthday.
OL,12,FA wartime hero who saved one of Wales'
OL,13,Fmost historic buildings from burning
OL,14,Fdown as a teenager, has been honoured
OL,15,Fon his 100th birthday.
OL,17,FRonald Brignall lives at a care home
OL,18,Fnear Brighton and his courageous
OL,19,Fsecret was only recently discovered by
OL,20,Fhis family after nearly 83 years.
