OL,3,CWartime hero who saved famed building
OL,4,Cgrins as he is honoured on 100th
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FRonald was just 16 years old when,
OL,8,Fduring a Second World War air raid, he
OL,9,Fscaled Cardiff's City Hall with one
OL,10,F12Ib sandbag clamped between his teeth
OL,11,Fand another under his arm.
OL,13,FHe was cheered on as he climbed back
OL,14,Fup a 25ft drain pipe with a fire hose,
OL,15,Falso gripped in his teeth.
OL,17,FOnly about 10 minutes after springing
OL,18,Finto action, Ronald finished putting
OL,19,Fout the fire and saved the building
OL,20,Ffrom destruction.
