OL,7,FSpeaking to a local paper at the time,
OL,8,FRonald's only comment was that his jaw
OL,9,Fwas sore from carrying the sandbag and
OL,10,Fthat he had ruined his suit.
OL,12,FA 100th birthday party was held for
OL,13,FRonald, which his son, daughter and
OL,14,Fother care home residents attended.
OL,16,FWATCH: Ronald's son and daughter, Ian
OL,17,Fand Sue, speak about their father's
OL,18,Fsecret heroics.
