OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FThe centenarian smiled as his birthday
OL,8,Fwas celebrated, surrounded by birthday
OL,9,Fcards and memorabilia.
OL,11,FThis included contemporary newspaper
OL,12,Fclippings, old photographs and a
OL,13,Fcommendatory letter from his then-
OL,14,Femployer, who gave the young man some
OL,15,Fmoney to put towards a new suit.
OL,17,FThe Lord Mayor of Cardiff, Bablin
OL,18,FMolik, travelled to Sussex to present
OL,19,FRonald with a framed certificate on
OL,20,Fbehalf of Cardiff Council.
