OL,7,FHe took part in the last major
OL,8,Fairborne operation of the war
OL,9,F(Operation Varsity) the following year
OL,10,Fas a rear-gunner on a Whitley and
OL,11,FHalifax bomber.
OL,13,FThree RAF representatives handed a
OL,14,Fcongratulatory letter to the Air Force
OL,15,Fveteran, who was wearing medals
OL,16,Fawarded to him as a result of his
OL,17,Fservice.
