OL,7,FMs Molik also gave him a Welsh rugby
OL,8,Fshirt, signed by all of the players,
OL,9,Fsaying she was "honoured to meet a
OL,10,Fliving legend" and was delighted to
OL,11,Fpresent Ronald with his belated honour.
OL,13,FA singer performed for the care home
OL,14,Fresidents, singing Elvis Presley songs
OL,15,Fand other hits from the 1950s and '60s.
OL,17,FRonald's son said he had rediscovered
OL,18,Fthe old newspaper clippings when he
OL,19,F"delved through his belongings to try
OL,20,Fand find some old photos" to display
OL,21,Fon his father's birthday.
