OL,7,FHe said when he had asked his father
OL,8,Fwhy he had never told anyone about the
OL,9,FCardiff City Hall fire, he replied:
OL,10,F"Well, it just never seemed relevant."
OL,12,F"I think he's a very brave, very stoic
OL,13,Fchap," he added.
OL,15,FHe said: "Dad's a little frail now, as
OL,16,Fyou'd expect from someone who is 100,
OL,17,Fbut I know he is thrilled to have this
OL,18,Frecognition and the certificate from
OL,19,Fthe council.
